		flat (MIDDLE - FBALANCE) 0 [heading UPWARD]
		curl (MIDDLE - FBALANCE) (CAP - FHOOK)
		straight.right.end (MIDDLE - FBALANCE + HOOKX) (CAP - HALFSTROKE - fovershoot) [heading RIGHTWARD]
